</style>

<main class="inside">
    <div class="box">
        <div class="box-box">
            <span style="font-size: 23px; font-weight: 500;">Punishment Policy</span>
            <div class="box-box-box">
                <span style="font-size: 18px; color: #2d0065">Format:</span>
                <p>
                    <strong>Rule broke:</strong> (Refer to the corresponding TOS rule)
                    <br />
                    <strong>Sanction:</strong> Disabling the account for X time / Ban the account / Removal of views / IP ban / Warn / Removal of VIP permissions\ <br />
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>First Time:</strong></li>
                        <li><strong>Second time:</strong></li>
                        <li><strong>Third time:</strong></li>
                    </ul>
                    <strong>How to appeal:</strong> (Always ticket system) <br />
                    (Big actions cannot be appealed) (Like uploading gore, NSFW, and more)
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="box-box-box">
                <p>
                    <strong>Rule broke:</strong> Receiving Views - Spamming the API with small requests <br />
                    <strong>Sanction:</strong> <br />
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>First time:</strong> Warning + Removal of views gained through spamming + Disabling of the account for 1 day</li>
                        <li><strong>Second time:</strong> Ban the account</li>
                        <li><strong>Third time:</strong> IP ban of the account.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <strong>How to appeal:</strong> Appeal through the ticket system within 24 hours of receiving the sanction.
                </p>
            </div>
